703322f-a.title: Brooklyn: Brighton Beach Avenue - 2nd Street (West)
703322f-a.text:
(1)
Brighton Beach Ave., north side, between West 2nd and West 3rd Streets. This B.M.T. right of way is a continuation of Brighton Beach Ave.
December 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(2)
The same, showing to the right P.5. No. 100 under construction.
January 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
